data.description: One floor living at it's finest! Come enjoy all this cozy ranch has to offer. The metal roof was replaced only 3 years ago, as was the hot water tank.  There is new trim and flooring throughout the house, along with new interior doors. The kitchen is nicely updated and has plenty of cabinet and counter space to suit all of your needs, plus has the laundry hookups right around the corner to make washing the clothes a breeze. The dining room and living room are open, allowing for a nice space to entertain. Outside you'll find a detached garage, with a covered side patio. The fenced yard also includes a wonderful fire pit area for enjoying evenings in the outdoors with friends and family. Pick up the phone and call to schedule your showing today!
